## 1. Application Overview

**PaySitters RECOVER** is a self-service consumer-facing arrears resolution portal built by Nevado AI on the Portica platform. It allows consumers who have past-due balances to independently resolve their debt through three mechanisms: a lump-sum settlement offer (at a discount), a fixed 3-installment plan, or a fully custom payment schedule they build themselves with a 1–12 month slider. The product is positioned as a non-adversarial, "no phone calls, no judgment" alternative to traditional collection calls.

The entry point is an SMS link sent by the collection agency (Southwest Recovery Services / SWRS in the demo). Consumers tap the link on their phone, verify their identity, confirm their contact info, select a resolution plan, connect a payment method (ACH or debit card), and are then shown a post-enrollment dashboard.

**Primary users:** Consumers with past-due telecom/utility balances receiving outreach from a debt collection agency.
**Secondary users:** Collection agencies (creditors) who configure and brand the portal (B2B view — not accessible in this build).

