## 4. User Flow Maps

### Flow 1: Complete Consumer Resolution Journey

```
[SMS received on phone]
        ↓
[1] SMS Entry Mockup (/)
    → Tap "See Your Options" RCS card
        ↓
[2] Welcome Screen (/r/m4r1a)
    Shows: Agency branding, account balance, 3 benefit callouts
    → Tap "Get Started →"
        ↓
[3] Identity Verification (Step 1/3)
    Fill: SSN last 4 + DOB + Postal Code
    → Tap "Find My Account →"
        ↓ (if match found)
[4] Confirm Details (Step 2/3)
    Review/edit: Name, Email, Phone, Address
    Check: Terms & Privacy checkbox
    → Tap "Confirm & Continue →"
        ↓
[5] Choose Resolution (Step 3/3)
    Select one of three paths:
    ├── [A] Settle Now → "Confirm Settlement →"
    ├── [B] Pay in 3 Installments → "Confirm 3-Payment Plan →"
    └── [C] Build Your Own Plan → Slider Screen
                ↓ (all paths)
[6] Review & Pay
    Review plan summary
    Select payment method (ACH or Debit Card)
    → Tap "Set Up Payment →"
        ↓
[7] Confirmation / You're All Set!
    Shows receipt details
    → Tap "View My Dashboard →"
        ↓
[8] Dashboard
    Post-enrollment home with payment info
```

### Flow 2: Settlement Option (Option A)

Step 5 → Select "Settle Now" card → Green checkmark appears on radio → "Confirm Settlement →" button animates in below card → Tap → Step 6 (Review & Pay) shows "Settlement · 1 payments" plan card with $208.50 total.

### Flow 3: 3-Installment Plan (Option B)

Step 5 → Select "Pay in 3 Installments" (pre-highlighted as BEST VALUE) → "Confirm 3-Payment Plan →" appears → Tap → Step 6 with 3 × $115.84 plan.

### Flow 4: Custom Payment Plan Slider (Option C)

Step 5 → Click "Build Your Own Plan" / "Customize →" → **Build Your Plan screen**:
- Default: 6 months ($57.92/mo)
- Drag slider or tap chips: 1mo / 2mo / 3mo / 6mo / 9mo / 12mo
- Live recalculation: monthly amount and final payment date update instantly
- Summary row updates: "N payments starting April 1, 2026 · $X.XX/mo · $0 fees"
- Tap "Use This Plan →" → Step 6 (Review & Pay)

### Flow 5: Identity Verification Failure

Step 3 → Enter wrong SSN/DOB/ZIP → Tap "Find My Account →" → Network request fires → After ~2s delay: pink-red error banner appears: "We couldn't match your information. Please double-check and try again." → User can retry.

### Flow 6: CoverLink / Referral

- From Dashboard → Tap "Share Now" on Refer a Friend card
- The CoverLink flow uses route `/cover/:linkId`
- If link is valid: recipient sees a contribution UI (text in bundle: "Share Cover Link" dialog with "Share this link with family or friends. They can help pay your {billName} balance without seeing your personal financial details.")
- If link is expired/invalid: Shows "This link is no longer available." error page

### Flow 7: Bill Discovery / Add Bills

From Dashboard → "Add These Bills →" CTA → Presumably leads to PaySitters main app bill-linking flow at `/bills/add` or `/onboarding/bank-bills` (not directly accessible in RECOVER module context).

